The problem is, when trying to sort them, they move off at exactly the same time, giving no opportunity to seperate them. If I had another group member cast root or snare on one then I could seperate them, but then that group member would get agro.<br>
Alternatively, I could use those silk net things to snare them myself, but that's a little pricey for an untwinked level 26.<br>
So, what I want to know before I go and get my party wiped out, is whether or not another party member tagging one of the pair as I pull past will add them to the hate list of the other mob that I still have in tow, and if so, how far off it's return path do they have to be before it won't come after them when I feign?<br>
