<br>
a few ways to split them are:<br>
<br>
use a wall to try to warp them<br>
try to get one stuck on a wierd pathing if one is near<br>
if outside use harmony, inside try chanter/bard lure (note could pull both if resisted)<br>
or just pull em both and get them controlled (root park, mez, charm, fear outdoors, just let things happen etc)<br>
