<br>
Yes, the tagged mob will pass aggro and hate to the other one.<br>
<br>
If you're in the old world it'll go back for the tagger instantly you FD, and in Kunark Velious or Luclin you have to be so far away I'd suggest you just kite the mob round in circles instead - provided it's a non-nuker and you have sow - till your group's finished off the first one.<br>
<br>
You could try range pulling the mobs with sneak on, trying to angle yourself (if possible) so the mob you're not pulling isn't facing you and is on the far side of the spawn; sometimes this helps.<br>
<br>
Otherwise, I'd say the techniques used to separate mobs with this kind of FD behaviour at higher levels tend to take too much time to be practicable at your level.<br>
